                    "text": "The \"Scheme of Providing Assistance to Encourage Farmers for Adoption of Organic Farming\" introduced by the Agriculture, Farmers Welfare and Cooperation Department, Gujarat, aims to encourage farmers to adopt organic farming by offering financial incentives for certification, registration, and input costs. It helps maintain soil fertility, supports biological input management, and promotes traditional knowledge. "
